Package Agents

Contains the different algorithms used during the inference/learning stage of the workflow.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InferenceAgent
    A general interface for describing different inference/learning agents.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicInferenceAgent
    The example inference agent (Agent 3).
    BetterInferenceAgent
    The improved inference agent (Agent 4).
    BlindfoldedAgent
    This is the blindfolded agent from Project 1 (Agent 1).
    FourNeighbourAgent
    This is the agent that can see from Project 1 (Agent 2).
    PerfectInferenceAgent
    An inference agent that can infer everything possible from the KB (used for comparison purposes).
